  operates on the caller's own (userId,agentId) mirror — no cross-tenant exposure.
- Supply chain: only @ax/workspace-git-core (workspace:* internal) added as an @ax/ipc-core
  devDependency for the F-1 integration test — no external package, no version range, no install
  scripts. No other package.json changes.

